{"title":"安全岛","authors":["谢先云"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢先云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，安全岛——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个大字红光耀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，安全岛——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐落在街中人行道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浅黄色的栅栏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不低也不高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几米宽的面积，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不大也不小。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车来人往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽阔的长街涌波涛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在小岛躲车辆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它象一块安全礁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，安全礁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁想得这样妙？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，安全礁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁想得这样好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，一辆“红旗”车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开进繁华街道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"礼让过街行人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"减低车速慢跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您想到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——社员进城少；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——街中需设岛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家大事知多少？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众过街也想到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全岛上忆总理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中火苗熊熊烧……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}